s to choose their initial password when registering (note that this setting is a mirror of the <a href=\"!settings\">Require e-mail verification when a visitor creates an account</a> setting, and is merely here for convenience). If selected, users will be assigned to the role below. They will not be assigned to the \'authenticated user\' role until they confirm their e-mail address by following the link in their registration e-mail. It is HIGHLY recommended that you set up a \'pre-authorized\' role with limited permissions for this purpose. <br />NOTE: If you enable this feature, you should edit the <a href=\"!settings\">Welcome (no approval required)</a> text.','','7.12'),(6403,'/admin/config/system/logintoboggan?render=overlay','default','Non-authenticated role','','7.12'),(6404,'/admin/config/system/logintoboggan?render=overlay','default','If \"Set password\" is selected, users will be able to login before their e-mail address has been authenticated. Therefore, you must choose a role for new non-authenticated users -- you may wish to <a href=\"!url\">add a new role</a> for this purpose. Users will be removed from this role and assigned to the \"authenticated user\" role once they follow the link in their welcome e-mail. <strong>WARNING: changing this setting after initial site setup can cause undesirable results, including unintended deletion of users -- change with extreme caution!</strong>','','7.12'),(6405,'/admin/config/system/logintoboggan?render=overlay','default','Never delete','','7.12'),(6406,'/admin/config/system/logintoboggan?render=overlay','default','1 Day','','7.12'),(6407,'/admin/config/system/logintoboggan?render=overlay','default','2 Days','','7.12'),(6408,'/admin/config/system/logintoboggan?render=overlay','default','3 Days','','7.12'),(6409,'/admin/config/system/logintoboggan?render=overlay','default','4 Days','','7.12'),(6410,'/admin/config/system/logintoboggan?render=overlay','default','5 Days','','7.12'),(6411,'/admin/config/system/logintobo